SUBENT        D1079001   20251001   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                  8         16
TITLE      Measurement of secondary neutron spectra and the
            total yield from 18O(p,Xn) reaction
AUTHOR     (M.Zmeskal, M.Kostal, O.Lebeda, V.Zach, R.Behal,
            T.Czakoj, J.Simon, E.Novak, Z.Matej)
REFERENCE  (J,RPC,229,112431,2025)
INSTITUTE  (3CZRUJV,3CZRCTI,3CZRUJF)
           (3CZRCZR) Masaryk University, Brno
FACILITY   (CYCLO,3CZRUJF) U-120M cyclotron
SAMPLE     (8-O-18,ENR=0.98)
           Phial (5.5 mm inner diameter,  26 mm length, 2.3 ml
            volume, 25 um havar window) filled with water
            enriched to 98% with 18O and pressurized to 2E+5 Pa,
            thicker than the full stopping length of protons
STATUS     (APRVD) Proofread by Marek Zmeskal (2025-10-01)
HISTORY    (20251001R) On. Data received from Marek Zmeskal.
           (20251001C) On
ENDBIB              16
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           19
SUBENT        D1079002   20251001   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                  4         11
REACTION   (8-O-CMP(P,X)0-NN-1,,PY/DA/DE,,TT/CH)
            water enriched with 18O
DETECTOR   (SCIN) stilbene crystal (1 x 1 cm) which centre was
            located at a distance of 203 cm from the entrance
            of the water target
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Uncertainty due to
           - statistics
           - deconvolution
           - energy calibration
STATUS     (TABLE,,M.Zmeskal,J,RPC,229,112431,2025)
            Spectra in Fig.5 renormalized by Marek Zmeskal
